full_summary:
### Government Tender Announcement

#### Tender Title
Emergency Breathing System In-Service Support

#### Solicitation Number
W6399-23LK64/C

#### Public Tender Notice Date
2024-01-15

#### Tender Closing Date
2024-03-20, 14:00:00 (EDT)

#### Tender Status
Expired

#### Contract Overview
The Department of National Defence has a requirement for the provision of inspection, maintenance, and repair services for the Emergency Breathing System in-service support. The proposed work must comply with the technical requirements outlined in the Request for Proposal (RFP) solicitation document.

#### Trade Agreements
The requirement is subject to a preference for Canadian goods and/or services. The Crown retains the right to negotiate with suppliers on any procurement.

#### Procurement Information

* Tender Description: The RFP solicitation document provides detailed information on the technical requirements and evaluation criteria.
* Contact Information:
	+ Matthew Yaraskovitch, Contracting Authority
	+ Email: [matthew.yaraskovitch@forces.gc.ca](mailto:matthew.yaraskovitch@forces.gc.ca)
	+ Phone: (613) 945-2762
* Documents:
	+ RFP Solicitation Document (English): [https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/29318/2.-w6399-23-lk64c-rfp-en.pdf](https://canadabuys.canada.ca/sites/default/files/webform/tender_notice/29318/2.-w6399-23-lk64c-rfp-en.pdf)
